.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解大家咁肯定呢批蟲係頭一批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70754b1455add2d51a4d1f9502c344ca8a3d9748","tid":249700,"uid":49395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T23:43:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解大家咁肯定呢批蟲係頭一批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4173100f92201b704864513ca4504d6e64f8715d","tid":249700,"uid":75211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T00:09:36.000Z","msg":"1. 臭屁蟲<br />\n<br />\n不少新界區居民都可能會在家中看見臭屁蟲產下的卵，如不理會就會如上圖般孵化成黑色幼蟲，惡臭難聞。<br />\n<br />\n陳澤森指，臭屁蟲雖然氣味刺鼻，但不算害蟲，亦不會傳播傳染病，市區內數量增加可能與市區綠化計劃有關，屋邨多了植物，因此在新界區逐漸變得更為常見。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，臭味是臭屁蟲的防禦機制之一，另外臭屁蟲的成蟲或蟲卵感到危險時，亦會分泌出具刺激性的針液，同樣惡臭難聞，接觸皮膚時可能導致敏感甚至損傷。<br />\n<br />\n他建議，如市民發現其蹤影，可用硬卡紙將其掃走，又或用毛巾包裹好，小心將蟲或卵拿走，切勿把它們弄穿。"},{"pid":"c1c95ec7a3584f75944109a3947d5f8c3dc11a80","tid":249700,"uid":11284